package concept

root_mean_square_speed: {
  content: #"""
    The *root-mean-square speed* is defined as:

    $ v_"rms" = sqrt(⟨v^2⟩) $

    From the equation related average translational kinetic energy and temperature
    we can obtain:

    $ 1/2 m v_"rms"^2 = 3/2 k T space.en => v_"rms" = sqrt((3 k T)/m)
      = sqrt((3 R T)/M) $
  """#
  related: [
    "concept/average-translational-kinetic-energy",
    "concept/temperature-from-microscopic"
  ]
}